rajawali.animation

Class SlerpAnimation3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • rajawali.renderer.AFrameTask
      • rajawali.animation.Animation3D
        • rajawali.animation.SlerpAnimation3D

  • public class SlerpAnimation3D
extends Animation3D
    Performs spherical linear interpolation (SLERP) animation between two Vector3s. Example usage: 
    
 SlerpAnimation3D anim = new SlerpAnimation3D(pointOnSphere1, pointOnSphere1);
 anim.setDuration(1000);
 anim.setInterpolator(new AccelerateDecelerateInterpolator());
 anim.setTransformable3D(myObject);
 registerAnimation(anim);
 anim.play();
    Author:
    dennis.ippel
